OL,3,COperation Coastwatch begins in summer
OL,4,Ccrackdown on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,Fare urging the public to "respect
OL,7,Ftheir communities and coastline" in a
OL,8,Fcrackdown on anti-social behaviour.
OL,10,FThe annual effort will see extra
OL,11,Fpatrols and beach wardens along
OL,12,Fcoastline to ensure it is safe for
OL,13,Fresidents and visitors as the summer
OL,14,Fseason gets underway.
OL,16,FPolice say there will be particular
OL,17,Ffocus on premises selling alcohol to
OL,18,Fthose under the age of 18.
