OL,3,COperation Coastwatch begins in summer
OL,4,Ccrackdown on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FAny retailer found to be doing so will
OL,7,Flose their licence in a bid to "send a
OL,8,Fclear message".
OL,10,FIt follows reports of antisocial
OL,11,Fbehaviour such as littering and
OL,12,Funderage drinking following end-of-
OL,13,Fterm celebrations last year.
OL,15,FParents and carers are now being
OL,16,Fencouraged to speak with their
OL,17,Fchildren about their plans, what they
OL,18,Fare doing and the potential
OL,19,Fconsequences of involvement in anti-
OL,20,Fsocial behaviour.
