OL,3,COperation Coastwatch begins in summer
OL,4,Ccrackdown on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FThe scheme is part of a partnership
OL,7,Fbetween Northumbria Police, North
OL,8,FTyneside Council and Nexus.
OL,10,FDan Whyte, Chief Superintendent for
OL,11,FNorth Tyneside, said: "We know that
OL,12,Flocal residents and businesses have
OL,13,Fconcerns around anti-social behaviour
OL,14,Fand disorder, and we want to reassure
OL,15,Fthem that we, along with our partners,
OL,16,Fare here to continue to support and
OL,17,Fprotect communities.
OL,26,@sD@WOU
