OL,3,COperation Coastwatch begins in summer
OL,4,Ccrackdown on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,F"I want to be clear that any pockets
OL,7,Fof disorder will be dealt with swiftly
OL,8,Fand robustly. We won't tolerate people
OL,9,Fnegatively impacting the experience of
OL,10,Fothers.
OL,12,F"The warmer weather isn't a green
OL,13,Flight for people to stop obeying the
OL,14,Flaw. We all have a responsibility to
OL,15,Fone another, and everyone deserves to
OL,16,Fhave a good time without worrying
OL,17,Fabout the actions of others.
OL,19,F"As ever, we'd ask the wider community
OL,20,Fto help us and continue to show their
OL,21,Fsupport."
