OL,3,COperation Coastwatch begins in summer
OL,4,Ccrackdown on anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FPreventative work to discourage anti-
OL,7,Fsocial behaviour is also being rolled
OL,8,Fout on transport links to the coast,
OL,9,Fwith the police working with the metro
OL,10,Foperators Nexus.
OL,12,FErika Allen, Quality, Health, Safety,
OL,13,FSecurity and Environment Director at
OL,14,FNexus, said: "Metro is a major gateway
OL,15,Finto the North Tyneside coastline over
OL,16,Fthe summer months, and we want people
OL,17,Fto come and enjoy it, but we don't
OL,18,Fwant a minority of troublemakers to
OL,19,Fspoil it for everyone else.
